  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Recyclability-grade declaration observation. Captures the",
    "moment a notified body / conformity-assessment lab assigns the",
    "PPWR Annex II recyclability grade (A / B / C) to a packaging",
    "SKU. The grade itself is a static attribute of the product and",
    "is therefore carried on the product entry inside",
    "masterDataAvailableFor; the event records WHEN the declaration",
    "happened, WHO declared it, and against which methodology.",
    "",
    "PPWR Reg 2025/40 Art. 6 + Annex II (recyclability grading).",
    "Grade B / C carry phase-out dates (B from 2030, C by 2038).",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: dpp=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,",
    "                              ppwr=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/ppwr/",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
